node.text:
How cute? 🙈 We can post your pictures in our account. Check the link in our bio for more info: @viewfervor (viewfervor.com)

Animals never forget those who love and care for them - no matter how much time may pass 🙏🏼💚@zwfmiami @limbanizwf @mariowildlife @misstyflower

You guys know how big of a believer I am in the human/animal bond. I believe that this planet was meant for us all. I hate seeing animals being poached and habitats being destroyed through human greed. Somewhere along the line, we as humans, have stopped caring for wildlife. We started placing ourselves first, forgetting about the planet and animals in the process. Videos like this prove otherwise. They show the connection between humans who place animals first and the love that is possible. They show that we are meant to coexist, and I hope they cause people to rethink the value and importance that we place on the planet and animals that we share it with. Earth is meant for us all 🌎🌍🌏🙌🏼💪🏼

📽 @gabaaa_31 via @maxstrong

Welcome to paradise with @adrianbaias and @florina__toma 😍 Wanna see your pictures posted in our account? Apply for a feature on viewfervor.com (link in my bio: @viewfervor)

At Calilo, a tranquil retreat - a visionary conservation project that offers an escape from the clamour and the crowds. Think sun-drenched seclusion surrounded by an ancient olive-pricked landscape - @nature and art at its heart. Find yourself and all you need in a land in deep connection with everything.

Who would you share this hideout with? 😌

📽 @adrianbaias w/ @florina__toma
📍 Calilo Hotel, Ios, Greece
🎶 Henry Mancini - Lujon

2. @bei.bei.wei. South Kensington Townhouse in London. 
3. @donnadotanphoto. Cobble Hill Townhouse by @workshopapd
4. @jacob_elliott. 50 Oakwood Residence by @stanley_saitowitz
5. @peteraaron. West Village Townhouse by @ramsarchitects
